                    <p>A project for CS186 at Mills College, CitizensOrg is a web application that helps facilitates neighborhood political organizing. After the 2016
                    election, we wanted to create a tool that made political organizing easy; a platform where people could schedule meetings and share information.
                    Users will be able to login, create a group, invite members to their group, or join a group. An additional feature enables users to
                    look up their Congresspeople by zipcode.
            
                    </p>
